OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,FThe widow of one of the founding
OL,8,Fmembers of the Notting Hill Carnival
OL,9,Fhas said "work still needs to be done"
OL,10,Fto educate the public about its
OL,11,Fmeaning.
OL,13,FThe event is an annual Caribbean
OL,14,Fcarnival which launched in 1966 as a
OL,15,Fcultural celebration of culture and
OL,16,Fthe freedom of slaves after
OL,17,Femancipation.
OL,26,@qD@JOUqD@fO]
