OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,FThe Notting Hill Carnival began after
OL,8,Frace riots in the area and has since
OL,9,Fgrown to attract around two million
OL,10,Fpeople annually.
OL,12,FOne of its founders was Vernon
OL,13,FWilliams who emigrated from Trinidad
OL,14,Fand Tobago in the 1960s.
OL,16,FThis year marks 60 years of the event,
OL,17,Fwith his widow Allyson Williams also
OL,18,Fbeing involved herself for 45 years.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
