CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1784371686
OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,FMs Williams said she was once shocked
OL,8,Fto discover many people ` even those
OL,9,Fliving locally ` had no idea of the
OL,10,Fsignificance of the event.
OL,12,FRecalling a conversation she once had
OL,13,Fwith a local resident after giving a
OL,14,Fspeech at the launch of the carnival,
OL,15,FMs Williams said she was told at the
OL,16,Ftime by the woman: "I had no idea it
OL,17,Fmeant anything to anybody. I just
OL,18,Fthought it was a big party or
OL,19,Fsomething."
OL,26,@xD@TOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
