CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1784371686
OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,FThe woman then told her: "I have lived
OL,8,Fhere for 30 years, and I had no idea.
OL,9,FIt never dawned on me to ask. It never
OL,10,Fdawned on me to find out why it was so
OL,11,Fimportant. We just thought it was a
OL,12,Fnuisance two days of the year."
OL,14,FYears later, Ms Williams says she
OL,15,Fbelieves that perception still exists
OL,16,Fbut she is doing her best to break it
OL,17,Fdown.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
