OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,F"We really need to keep educating the
OL,8,Fpublic and educating people all the
OL,9,Ftime about the significance of the
OL,10,Fcarnival," she said.
OL,12,F"We still have work to do."
OL,14,FCalling the carnival a "spectacle", Ms
OL,15,FWilliams also said it "celebrated the
OL,16,Flegacy and heritage" of the Caribbean
OL,17,Fcommunity and had always been a "very
OL,18,Fpowerful way of uniting the community".
