OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,F"It helps the Caribbean people to
OL,8,Fcelebrate their legacy and to pay
OL,9,Fhomage and respect to their ancestors
OL,10,Fwho died and suffered so much on our
OL,11,Fbehalf," she added.
OL,13,FThe Notting Hill Carnival is now
OL,14,FEurope's largest cultural event and
OL,15,Fthe world's largest carnival, with
OL,16,Forganisers also calling it a "symbol
OL,17,Fof unity".
OL,19,FGladwin Wright is one of the longest
OL,20,Frunning sound system operators in the
OL,21,FUK and the Carnival.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@HO]xD@^OUyD@IO]
