OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,FSince first attending nearly 40 years
OL,8,Fago, Mr Wright said he "looks forward
OL,9,Fto it every year".
OL,11,F"I've never seen a bad carnival except
OL,12,Fa couple of times it rained all day,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,F"Every year is good, and yet every
OL,16,Fyear seems better."
OL,18,FDescribing the importance of Notting
OL,19,FHill Carnival, Mr Wright admitted he
OL,20,Feven preferred it to Christmas.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@QO]sD@AOUtD@eO]wD@AOUxD@SO]
