OL,3,CWork still needed to educate on
OL,4,CNotting Hill Carnival, says co-
OL,5,Cfounder's widow
OL,7,F"I'll say that. To me, you'd have to
OL,8,Fput 10 Christmases together to grab
OL,9,Fthe vibration a carnival gives me.
OL,11,F"And I've heard a lot of people said
OL,12,Fthat. There's a lot of joy and
OL,13,Fanticipation surrounding the day."
OL,15,FThe 2026 Notting Hill Carnival runs
OL,16,Ffrom August 29 to 31.
